# section 1

Lab 1: Data Exploration and Visualization

Theme: Exploring and Visualizing Dental Health Data

* Exercise 1: Use data visualization techniques to visualize qualitative data related to dental health, such as patient demographics and dental treatment preferences.

* Exercise 2: Visualize quantitative data related to dental health, such as statistical distributions of cavity occurrences or tooth decay rates.

* Exercise 3: Create time series visualizations to analyze trends in dental health data over time, such as the prevalence of dental caries or plaque detection rates.
